---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. delete a branch
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 hamster]$git branch -d hamster-2.0-poc
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 hamster]$git push origin :hamster-2.0-poc  //remote delete a branch
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. merge from a branch, but only keep one commit 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
git checkout master
git merge --squash www
git commit -m "merge with www"
git push origin master
